revisions.description: The initial release of this management information module.

usdErxSystemAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdErxSystemAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Edge Routing Switch (ERX) System component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere ERX family of products.

usdErxSystemAgentV1.name: usdErxSystemAgentV1
usdErxSystemAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the ERX System component of the Unisphere Edge Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the ERX System component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 1.3 system release.
usdErxSystemAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in the Unisphere Edge Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when new slot information objects were added.

usdErxSystemAgentV2.name: usdErxSystemAgentV2
usdErxSystemAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the ERX System component of the Unisphere Edge Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the ERX System component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 2.x system releases.
usdErxSystemAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in the Unisphere Edge Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the timing group was added.

usdErxSystemAgentV3.name: usdErxSystemAgentV3
usdErxSystemAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the ERX System component of the Unisphere Edge Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the ERX System component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.0 system release.
usdErxSystemAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in the Unisphere Edge Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when memory management objects and notifications were added.

usdErxSystemAgentV4.name: usdErxSystemAgentV4
usdErxSystemAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the ERX System component of the Unisphere Edge Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the ERX System component was
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.2 system release.
usdErxSystemAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in the Unisphere Edge Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when thermal protection support was added.

usdErxSystemAgentV5.name: usdErxSystemAgentV5
usdErxSystemAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the ERX System component of the Unisphere Edge Routing
        Switch SNMP agent.  This version of the ERX System component is
        supported in the Unisphere RX 3.3 and subsequent system releases.
usdErxSystemAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in the Unisphere Edge Routing Switch.
